---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
const title = "Schwab-TD Ameritrade Merger – Not a Done Deal";
const date = "2019-11-21";
---
<Layout title={title} description={`${title} — Newsletter from Sherwood Investments`}>
  <div class="relative text-white py-16 px-4 text-center" style="background: linear-gradient(rgba(19,40,64,0.78), rgba(19,40,64,0.78)), url('/banners/resources.jpg') center/cover no-repeat;">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-gold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm font-semibold mb-2">Newsletter</p>
      <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold mb-4">{title}</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm">{date}</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <a href="/resources" class="text-gold text-sm hover:underline">&larr; Back to Resources</a>
    <div class="mt-8 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed text-base">
      <p class="mb-4">Charles Schwab and TD Ameritrade announced on November 21, 2019 that they are in merger talks.  Here is the status and my thoughts.</p>
      <p class="mb-4">First, the merger is no sure thing.  There are potential antitrust issues.  These are two large firms and I can see regulators rejecting the merger.</p>
      <p class="mb-4">Second, the integration of the two firms is expected to take 18 to 36 months if/when the deal is approved</p>
      <p class="mb-4">Third, a merger will not have any affect on your investments held at TD Ameritrade.  Assuming that a merger does take place, the biggest difference you may notice is a change in the appearance of your statements and the online platform you log into.  But  it will take years to play out.</p>
      <p class="mb-4">Fourth, it is more likely that a merged company will rely more heavily on the technology and trading platform from TD Ameritrade since they are the recognized technology leader.</p>
      <p class="mb-4">Bottom Line</p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4 space-y-1"><li class="ml-4">I see the odds of a merger of the two giants at about 50-50.</li></ul>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4 space-y-1"><li class="ml-4">This will have no immediate impact.</li></ul>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4 space-y-1"><li class="ml-4">Any impact will be gradual.</li></ul>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4 space-y-1"><li class="ml-4">If there is a merger, it probably won’t be before 2022.</li></ul>
      <p class="mb-4">Stay tuned for further updates.</p>
      <p class="mb-4">Contact us
For additional information, please contact us.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-gray-100">
      <a href="/resources" class="text-gold hover:underline text-sm">&larr; Back to all newsletters</a>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
